\[G(\mathbf{x}_{t})=\tfrac{1}{\eta_{t}}\big{(}\mathbf{x}_{t}-\mathrm{proj}_{ \mathcal{X}}(\mathbf{x}_{t}-\eta_{t}\nabla f(\mathbf{x}_{t}))\big{)},\]

